content: I do not have access to information about tricky's upcoming albums or the details of their production process. however, in general, the production process behind an album involves various stages such as conceptualization, songwriting, composition, recording, mixing, mastering, and distribution. the specific production process may vary depending on the artist, their vision for the album, and the resources and technologies available to them. it can involve collaborations with other musicians, producers, and engineers, as well as incorporation of various sounds, instruments, and genres.
